prompts.frontCover: A vibrant watercolor painting of a romantic anniversary beach picnic at sunset. The scene is set on a soft, sandy beach with gentle waves lapping at the shore. A cozy, patterned picnic blanket is spread out, upon which the couple (Lao Lao and Jordan) are comfortably seated, leaning against each other in a sweet, relaxed pose. They are both smiling lovingly as they sip from unique boba teas served in hollowed-out coconut shells, complete with large boba straws. The setting sun casts a warm, golden and pink glow across the entire scene, with beautiful, bleeding watercolor hues of orange, purple, and yellow blending together in the sky and reflecting on the calm ocean water. A few stray palm leaves and scattered seashells tastefully frame the bottom corners of the composition. In the center of the image, written in a beautiful, flowing handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Happy Anniversary, my love". The overall style is soft-focus, dreamy, and filled with affection, captured in a flat 2D artistic illustration with soft edges and painterly textures.
